Switch Label
Instapage allows us to deliver a better experience as possible on our website by creating more user-friendly and intuitive landing pages. To do that, we collect some data to understand, to improve and adjust our website consequently.
Microsoft Clarity
Switch Label
We use Microsoft Clarity to analyze how users interact with our website, understand what we can improve and hence offer a better experience to our customers.
Hotjar
Switch Label
Collection of data relating to the behavior of users on the site and their devices for analysis related to the user experience
