Targeting Cookies
These cookies may be set through our site by our advertising partners. They may be used by those companies to build a profile of your interests and show you relevant adverts on other sites. They do not store directly personal information, but are based on uniquely identifying your browser and internet device. If you do not allow these cookies, you will experience less targeted advertising.
Bing.com
Switch Label
Bing.com allows us to better place our service when users search for specific keywords on Bing.com. In this way we can let us know better and acquire new customers.
Braze
Switch Label
We use a CRM tool called Braze to better manage the relationship with our customers. Thanks Braze, we can send customized messages, notifications and emails for marketing and informational purposes.
Facebook
Switch Label
We use Facebook to acquire and retain customers by displaying highly customized advertisings.
Floodlight
Switch Label
Floodlight is the Google Marketing Platform conversion tracking system.
My Visual IQ (myvisualiq.net)
Switch Label
Visual IQ Inc. is a marketing data platform that supports us in collecting information to create more efficient marketing campaigns, offline and online both.
Youtube
Switch Label
We use Youtube to acquire and retain customers by displaying highly customized advertisings.
